.SH BUGS
.B hsh
does not support:
.PP
- Command separators (;, &&, ||)
.br
- Pipes (|)
.br
- Redirections (<, >, >>)
.br
- Comments (#)
.br
- Command substitution
.br
- Wildcards (*, ?, [])
.br
- Variables expansion ($VAR)
.br
- Special characters (\\, ', ")
.br
- Alias
.br
- History
